{"tid":2141823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"位於旺角亞皆老街怡安閣的「Star Global」成為第三波疫情以來成員最多的染疫群組。","createTime":"2020-08-06T03:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T03:59:28.000Z","uid":504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2b413a7430ea19fd0a0f85fe3c756f53cf5070","tid":2141823,"uid":504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/q1kYxy?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2Fq1kYxy%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=8dcc3b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/q1kYxy?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n位於旺角亞皆老街怡安閣的直銷公司「Star Global」新增7人確診，染疫群組總人數升上52，成為本港自7月5日爆發第三波疫情以來，成員最多的染疫群組。"}]}